creating Subsets
df1=df[['Page total likes','Category']].loc[0:15]
df1
df2=df[['Page total likes','Category']].loc[16:25]
df2
df3=df[['Page total likes','Category']].loc[31:35]
df3

merging
merged=pd.concat([df1,df2,df3])
merged

